Package: WRTDStidal
Type: Package
Title: Weighted regression for water quality evaluation in tidal waters
Version: 0.0.5.9000
Date: 2015-04-16
Author: Marcus W. Beck [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Marcus W. Beck <beck.marcus@epa.gov>
Description: An adaptation for estuaries (tidal waters) of weighted regression on time, discharge, and season to evaluate trends in water quality time series, with specific application to chlorophyll  
